summary: This function retrieves the value(s) stored in an Autumn-style annotation.
returns: Return an immutable list containing the values stored in anno.
example-1: @Authors (%22Larry%22, %22Moe%22, %22Curly%22)%0Amodule Main in execution;%0A%0Aannotation Authors;%0A%0A@Start%0Adefun main (args : String[]) : void%0A{%0A    val anno = F::findAnnotation(class Main, class Authors);%0A%0A    val values = F::iter(anno);%0A%0A    F::printlns(values);%0A}
